    slug: "why-chasing-google-rankings-might-be-your-biggest-seo-mistake",
    title: "Why Chasing Google Rankings Might Be Your Biggest SEO Mistake",
    excerpt: "You know that feeling when you finally get a keyword to rank #1 on Google and you're checking your analytics like \"okay, where's the traffic?\" and it's... nowhe...",
    date: "2026-04-17",
